name: Jet Propulsion
description:
I took this photo through the plexiglass walls of an aquarium tank teeming with colorful jellyfish. The creatures are mesmerizing as they propel themselves effortlessly and gracefully, performing ballet-like maneuvers. 

About the View Portal
The ring-like portal that frames the image was digitally abstracted from the headlamp a 1963 Chrysler muscle car. The decorative “tabs” make for a unique presentation of all manner of subjects.
